column2: SELECT u.AGCNr, u.ra, u.dec, n.objid, n.distance, n.type, n.mode, o.ra as ra_near, o.dec as dec_near, o.u, o.g, o.r, o.i, o.z, o.specObjID into mydb.environment_# FROM mydb.udg1# as u    outer apply dbo.fGetNearbyObjAllEq(u.ra, u.dec, #) as n    left join GALAXY as o on n.objid = o.objid   where u.ra=# and u.dec = #
